                  </persName>
             deposed, that the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178204100083"></xptr> sacks were all his property, and that he saw them loaded at Trevallion's, the over night.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17820410-60-person750">
                  William
                   Whitehead
